{"id":357,"ayahs":[{"number":54,"arabic":"قُلْ أَطِيعُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ وَأَطِيعُوا۟ ٱلرَّسُولَ ۖ فَإِن تَوَلَّوْا۟ فَإِنَّمَا عَلَيْهِ مَا حُمِّلَ وَعَلَيْكُم مَّا حُمِّلْتُمْ ۖ وَإِن تُطِيعُوهُ تَهْتَدُوا۟ ۚ وَمَا عَلَى ٱلرَّسُولِ إِلَّا ٱلْبَلَٰغُ ٱلْمُبِينُ","translation":"Say: “Pay heed unto God, and pay heed unto the Apostle.” And if you turn away [from the Apostle, know that] he will have to answer only for whatever he has been charged with, and you, for what you have been charged with; but if you pay heed unto him, you will be on the right way. Withal, the Apostle is not bound to do more than clearly deliver the message [entrust­ed to him].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2845.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":51208,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51209,"position":2,"arabic":"أَطِيعُوا۟","translation":"\"তোমরা আনুগত্য করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51210,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51211,"position":4,"arabic":"وَأَطِيعُوا۟","translation":"ও তোমরা আনুগত্য করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51212,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلرَّسُولَ ۖ","translation":"রাসূলের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51214,"position":6,"arabic":"فَإِن","translation":"কিন্তু যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51215,"position":7,"arabic":"تَوَلَّوْا۟","translation":"তোমরা মুখ ফিরাও","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51216,"position":8,"arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا","translation":"তবে (জেনে রাখো) প্রকৃতপক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51217,"position":9,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"তার উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51218,"position":10,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51219,"position":11,"arabic":"حُمِّلَ","translation":"তাকে (দায়িত্ব) ভার দেয়া হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51220,"position":12,"arabic":"وَعَلَيْكُم","translation":"আর তোমাদের উপর (দায়িত্ব)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51221,"position":13,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51222,"position":14,"arabic":"حُمِّلْتُمْ ۖ","translation":"তোমাদের (দায়িত্ব) ভার দেয়া হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51224,"position":15,"arabic":"وَإِن","translation":"আর যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51225,"position":16,"arabic":"تُطِيعُوهُ","translation":"তার আনুগত্য করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51226,"position":17,"arabic":"تَهْتَدُوا۟ ۚ","translation":"তোমরা সঠিক পথ পাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51228,"position":18,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51229,"position":19,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"(দায়িত্ব) উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51230,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱلرَّسُولِ","translation":"রাসূলের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51231,"position":21,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51232,"position":22,"arabic":"ٱلْبَلَـٰغُ","translation":"পৌঁছান (বিধান)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51233,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱلْمُبِينُ","translation":"সুস্পষ্টভাবে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/024_054_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51234,"position":24,"arabic":"٥٤","translation":"(৫৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":55,"arabic":"وَعَدَ ٱللَّهُ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ مِنكُمْ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَيَسْتَخْلِفَنَّهُمْ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ كَمَا ٱسْتَخْلَفَ ٱلَّذِينَ مِن قَبْلِهِمْ وَلَيُمَكِّنَنَّ لَهُمْ دِينَهُمُ ٱلَّذِى ٱرْتَضَىٰ لَهُمْ وَلَيُبَدِّلَنَّهُم مِّنۢ بَعْدِ خَوْفِهِمْ أَمْنًۭا ۚ يَعْبُدُونَنِى لَا يُشْرِكُونَ بِى شَيْـًۭٔا ۚ وَمَن كَفَرَ بَعْدَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْفَٰسِقُونَ","translation":"God has promised those of you who have attained to faith and do righteous deeds that, of a certainty, He will cause them to accede to power on earth, even as He caused [some of] those who lived before them to accede to it; and that, of a certainty, He will firmly establish for them the religion which He has been pleased to bestow on them; and that, of a certainty, He will cause their erstwhile state of fear to be replaced by a sense of security [seeing that] they worship Me [alone], not ascribing divine powers to aught beside Me. But all who, after [having understood] this, choose to deny the truth - it is they, they who are truly iniquitous!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2846.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":51733,"position":1,"arabic":"وَعَدَ","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51734,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51735,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদেরকে) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51736,"position":4,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51737,"position":5,"arabic":"مِنكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মধ্য হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51738,"position":6,"arabic":"وَعَمِلُوا۟","translation":"ও কাজ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51739,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ","translation":"সৎ","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51740,"position":8,"arabic":"لَيَسْتَخْلِفَنَّهُمْ","translation":"অবশ্যই তিনি প্রতিনিধি  বানাবেন তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51741,"position":9,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51742,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51743,"position":11,"arabic":"كَمَا","translation":"যেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51744,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱسْتَخْلَفَ","translation":"প্রতিনিধি বানিয়েছিলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51745,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদেরকে) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51746,"position":14,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51747,"position":15,"arabic":"قَبْلِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের পূর্ব (ছিলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51748,"position":16,"arabic":"وَلَيُمَكِّنَنَّ","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই সুদৃঢ় করবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51749,"position":17,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51750,"position":18,"arabic":"دِينَهُمُ","translation":"তাদের দ্বীনকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51751,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51752,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱرْتَضَىٰ","translation":"তিনি পছন্দ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51753,"position":21,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51754,"position":22,"arabic":"وَلَيُبَدِّلَنَّهُم","translation":"ও অবশ্যই পরিবর্তিত করে দিবেন তাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51755,"position":23,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51756,"position":24,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"পর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51757,"position":25,"arabic":"خَوْفِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের ভয়-ভীতির","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51758,"position":26,"arabic":"أَمْنًۭا ۚ","translation":"নিরাপত্তায়","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51760,"position":27,"arabic":"يَعْبُدُونَنِى","translation":"আমারই তারা ইবাদাত করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51761,"position":28,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"(আর) না","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51762,"position":29,"arabic":"يُشْرِكُونَ","translation":"তারা শরীক করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51763,"position":30,"arabic":"بِى","translation":"সাথে আমার","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51764,"position":31,"arabic":"شَيْـًۭٔا ۚ","translation":"কোন কিছুরই","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51766,"position":32,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"আর যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51767,"position":33,"arabic":"كَفَرَ","translation":"অস্বীকার করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51768,"position":34,"arabic":"بَعْدَ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51769,"position":35,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51770,"position":36,"arabic":"فَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"অতঃপর ঐসবলোক","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51771,"position":37,"arabic":"هُمُ","translation":"তারাই","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51772,"position":38,"arabic":"ٱلْفَـٰسِقُونَ","translation":"সত্যত্যাগী","audioUrl":"wbw/024_055_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51773,"position":39,"arabic":"٥٥","translation":"(৫৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":56,"arabic":"وَأَقِيمُوا۟ ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ وَءَاتُوا۟ ٱلزَّكَوٰةَ وَأَطِيعُوا۟ ٱلرَّسُولَ لَعَلَّكُمْ تُرْحَمُونَ","translation":"Hence, [O believers,] be constant in prayer, and render the purifying dues, and pay heed unto the Apostle, so that you might be graced with God’s mercy.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2847.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":52137,"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَقِيمُوا۟","translation":"এবং তোমরা প্রতিষ্ঠা করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_056_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52138,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ","translation":"সালাত","audioUrl":"wbw/024_056_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52139,"position":3,"arabic":"وَءَاتُوا۟","translation":"আর দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/024_056_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52140,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلزَّكَوٰةَ","translation":"যাকাত","audioUrl":"wbw/024_056_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52141,"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَطِيعُوا۟","translation":"ও আনুগত্য করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_056_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52142,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلرَّسُولَ","translation":"রাসূলের","audioUrl":"wbw/024_056_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52143,"position":7,"arabic":"لَعَلَّكُمْ","translation":"যাতে তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_056_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52144,"position":8,"arabic":"تُرْحَمُونَ","translation":"তোমরা অনুগ্রহভাজন হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_056_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52145,"position":9,"arabic":"٥٦","translation":"(৫৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":57,"arabic":"لَا تَحْسَبَنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ مُعْجِزِينَ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ وَمَأْوَىٰهُمُ ٱلنَّارُ ۖ وَلَبِئْسَ ٱلْمَصِيرُ","translation":"[And] think not that those who are bent on denying the truth can elude [their final reckoning even if they remain unscathed] on earth: the fire is their goal [in the life to come] - and vile indeed is such a journey’s end!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2848.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":52665,"position":1,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52666,"position":2,"arabic":"تَحْسَبَنَّ","translation":"কখনও মনে করো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52667,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52668,"position":4,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52669,"position":5,"arabic":"مُعْجِزِينَ","translation":"তারা অক্ষমকারী (আল্লাহ্‌কে)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52670,"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52671,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52673,"position":8,"arabic":"وَمَأْوَىٰهُمُ","translation":"এবং তাদের আশ্রয়স্থল","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52674,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارُ ۖ","translation":"জাহান্নাম","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52676,"position":10,"arabic":"وَلَبِئْسَ","translation":"আর অবশ্যই (তা) অতি নিকৃষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52677,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْمَصِيرُ","translation":"প্রত্যাবর্তনস্থল","audioUrl":"wbw/024_057_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52678,"position":12,"arabic":"٥٧","translation":"(৫৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":58,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ لِيَسْتَـْٔذِنكُمُ ٱلَّذِينَ مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَٰنُكُمْ وَٱلَّذِينَ لَمْ يَبْلُغُوا۟ ٱلْحُلُمَ مِنكُمْ ثَلَٰثَ مَرَّٰتٍۢ ۚ مِّن قَبْلِ صَلَوٰةِ ٱلْفَجْرِ وَحِينَ تَضَعُونَ ثِيَابَكُم مِّنَ ٱلظَّهِيرَةِ وَمِنۢ بَعْدِ صَلَوٰةِ ٱلْعِشَآءِ ۚ ثَلَٰثُ عَوْرَٰتٍۢ لَّكُمْ ۚ لَيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ وَلَا عَلَيْهِمْ جُنَاحٌۢ بَعْدَهُنَّ ۚ طَوَّٰفُونَ عَلَيْكُم بَعْضُكُمْ عَلَىٰ بَعْضٍۢ ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ يُبَيِّنُ ٱللَّهُ لَكُمُ ٱلْءَايَٰتِ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ عَلِيمٌ حَكِيمٌۭ","translation":"O YOU who have attained to faith! At three times [of day], let [even] those whom you rightfully pos­sess, as well as those from among you who have not yet attained to puberty, ask leave of you [before intruding upon your privacy]: before the prayer of daybreak, and whenever you lay aside your garments in the middle of the day, and after the prayer of nightfall: the three occasions on which your nakedness is likely to be bared. Beyond these [occasions], neither you nor they will incur any sin if they move [freely] about you, attending to [the needs of] one another. In this way God makes clear unto you His mes­sages: for God is all-knowing, wise!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2849.mp3","surahId":24,"words":[{"id":53307,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_058_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53308,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/024_058_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53309,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/024_058_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53310,"position":4,"arabic":"لِيَسْتَـْٔذِنكُمُ","translation":"যেন তোমাদের (হ'তে) অনুমতি নেয়","audioUrl":"wbw/024_058_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53311,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তারা) যাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_058_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53312,"position":6,"arabic":"مَلَكَتْ","translation":"মালিক করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/024_058_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53313,"position":7,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের ডান হাত (অর্থাৎ দাস দাসী)","audioUrl":"wbw/024_058_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53314,"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","translation":